Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种经历就类似于你堕入睡眠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You experience it every night as you drift asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&H9B8F79&\fs14\b1\frz-22\pos(245.414,106.071)}复制手机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&H9B8F79&\fs14\b1\frz-22\pos(245.414,106.071)}未完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&H13005A&\fs14\b1\frz-22\pos(225.203,175.5)}海登・普赖斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&H544D53&\fs14\b1\frz-22\pos(225.203,175.5)}强制配对失败
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉浸书中  或者恍惚错过高速公路的出口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}focus on a book, or miss your exit on the F.D.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-准备好了吗  -我想是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Ready? - I think so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请拿起旁边的平板电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Please pick up the tablet beside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选一张最能代表你情绪的图像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and choose an image that speaks to your emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上你的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I want you to close your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在脑中想象那幅图像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and form a mental picture of that image.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象那些鸟儿  那片旷野\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Picture the birds, the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一只接着一只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象它们一一飞走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}picture them as they fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专心于呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Focus on your breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只鸟飞走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}One bird departs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着鸟一只只飞走  你越来越放松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And as each one goes, your relaxation increases
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越平静  越来越安宁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and you continue to feel calmer and more at rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两百块一小时  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}For 200 bucks an hour, Finch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别光打个巨贵的盹儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I hope you get more than an expensive nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要带你回到你这一生中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I want to take you back to a place in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最安全最舒适的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}where you were safe and comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能想想那个地方吗  冉先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Can you think of that place, Mr. Wren?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我童年时的卧室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My childhood bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  想想让你感觉安全的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now, I want you to think of all the ways it made you feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象得清楚一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Picture it clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墙壁是什么颜色的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What color were the walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登・普赖斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hayden Price--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上东区的认证催眠治疗师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}certified hypnotherapist to the Upper East Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做生日派对表演吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Does he do birthday parties?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那种催眠  里瑟先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's not that kind of hypnotism, Mr. Reese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他主要是服务于豪商巨贾和社会名流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He caters to wealthy businessmen and socialites.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愤怒管理  烟瘾戒断  如此之类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Anger management, smoking cessation, that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你还不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Or so you might think, if you didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的办公室是短期租借的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that the office was rented on a short-term lease,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他的认证资格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and that his certification
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找不到其颁发机构\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}doesn't come from any association I can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治疗期间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}During the therapy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想明白了海登问那些问题的含义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I became attuned to the kind of questions that Hayden was asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢的颜色  蓝色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A color that's favorable to you--blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,童年宠物的名字  哨兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The name of a childhood pet--Scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在钓鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was fishing--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要安全问题的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}getting answers to your security questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的银行账户忽然开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My bank account was suddenly signed up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自动循环捐款给一家非营利组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}for a recurring automatic donation to a nonprofit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫"美国癌症基金"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}called "The American Cancer Coalition Fund."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赌海登的名字肯定在那家非营利组织中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd be willing the wager that Hayden's name is on that nonprofit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  除非他的第二职业是当圣人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, unless he's moonlighting as a Samaritan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看这位是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd say we're dealing with a con artist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极聪明的贼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and a very clever thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你干嘛要合作啊  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So why'd you even play along, Finch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是告诉海登他想听到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I told Hayden what he wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我童年根本没宠物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't even have a pet as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我黑他的手机时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But when I went to bluejack his phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被墙在外了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it was blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有人黑进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Someone had already jacked it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是有人找他报仇了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}perhaps someone who's out to get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来最好是从他的客户着手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And his clients would be the best place to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我联系肖来帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll contact Shaw for back-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我得先去看看我们的客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but first I need to look in on our houseguest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格罗夫斯女士  里瑟先生一如既往等在楼上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}As before, Ms. Groves, Mr. Reese is upstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守着数目夸张的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}with an unhealthy number of firearms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要试图逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Please don't try to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的  哈罗德  就这么锁着我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Honestly, Harold, locking me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认居住条件不太理想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I admit that the accommodations are not ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但监禁你  对你有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But your confinement is for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德  是你的机器打电话给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold, your machine called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此事我还未能理出头绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}An event that I haven't fully reasoned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你喜怒无常  不惜伤人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But your unpredictability, your willingness to hurt others
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依旧危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}make you as dangerous as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法抗拒未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You can't fight the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带新书给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll bring you some new books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你奇怪为何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You wonder why
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不跟你说  却跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it won't talk to you like it talks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别嫉妒  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Don't be jealous, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈咪对我们俩都爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mom still loves us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然无法黑入海登手机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When bluejacking Hayden didn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就送了一篮点心聊表谢意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I sent him a basket of pastries as a thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然带监听器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Bugged, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太生她的气了  简直想杀了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm just so angry with her, I could kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着你越来越平静  那些感觉会消退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And those feelings will dissipate as you feel calmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛克斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Sykes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说你母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tell me about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出她的名字  大声点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Speak her name, out loud--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的全名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}her full name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-玛丽・夏克福德・赛克斯  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Mary Shackford Sykes. - Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&H282813&\b1\fs14\frz9\pos(148.692,135.643)}允许访问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来治疗起作用了  斯凡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It seems therapy has helped, Sven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好几个月没这么安稳地睡过觉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I haven't been able to sleep this well in months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你仍认为周围充满假货吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And do you still believe you're surrounded by phonies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很悲哀  是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sadly, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多亏你  我可以忘掉过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But thanks to you, I'm able to push past,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新用心经营我的古董生意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to rediscover the quality and craft of my antique business,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找我工作的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}search for the meaning in my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来海登这治疗师也不太烂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sounds like Hayden isn't a half-bad therapist after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天病人很多吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A lot of patients today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有怪人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Anybody weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一堆的母亲情结\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Wall-to-wally mommy issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致人产生烟瘾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Enough to make a man want to smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或睡眠不足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Or under-sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或暴饮暴食  或\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}or over-eat or--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Or?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩是谁  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who's the girl, Finch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫娜塔莉・波尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Her name is Natalie Boal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下城区的一家美术馆工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She works at an art gallery downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她从一年前开始接受海登的治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She started coming to Hayden for therapy a little over a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不只是治疗了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's more than therapy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是在工作  他爱上她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He isn't working her, he's in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就她看他的那眼神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And if she's making those eyes at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定不知道他那些犯罪勾当\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I bet she doesn't know about his criminal side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天  不再有病人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Someday, no more patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再有精神病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No more psychoses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再有傲慢的艺术品买家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No more snooty art buyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去机场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We just go to the airport...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞去世界的某个角落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Jet off to some corner of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱在哪里来着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}With what money, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱的问题交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Let me worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我赚够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And when I get enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只要你  我  天堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it's just you and me and paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登离开了  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hayden's on the move, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据他的日程计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}According to his schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今天没有预约了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}he doesn't have any more appointments today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他这是急着去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So where is he going so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- There you go. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情都顺利吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, is everything in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There's nothing to worry over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汇率对你有利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The exchange rates are in your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在S&L公司从出纳做起的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I started as a teller at that S&L, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干了十五年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}15 years I put in,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在居然给我降薪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and then they tell me I need to take a pay cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定给自己涨薪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So I decided they owed me a pay raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的五万美元  罗素先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Here's my $50,000, Mr. Russell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  开始进行吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Outstanding. Let's proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要崩了这小子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm so gonna shoot this punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情不太对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这里见你的联络人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We're meeting your contact here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里安静  远离那些想偷钱的贼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's quiet up here, and far from nosy thieves looking for cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这里唯一的贼是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No. The only thief here is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴克警探  纽约警局  欺诈调查科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Detective Decker, NYPD Fraud Investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来  白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hands up, sucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜猜他怎么诓你的  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can only guess what he got you for, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟你扯了那套汇率鬼话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He feed you that line of crap about the exchange rates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  把公文包慢慢递过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And you, pass me that briefcase very slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里瑟先生  肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Reese, Ms. Shaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么不干预\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Why aren't you intervening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Wait for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Is he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹着尾巴跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}With his tail between his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真骗了那小子两万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We really hooked that fish for 20 Gs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两万  不是五万吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}20? I thought it was 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你那一半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Here's your half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们快点儿走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now let's get the hell out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别等叫来真警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}before somebody calls the real cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登还有什么人不骗的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who isn't Hayden ripping off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子有两手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This guy's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直看你搅咖啡倒也可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can watch you nursing that coffee for just so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道  我给你电话是想问你近况  乔丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You should know I called, to check in on you, Joss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开开罚单  抓抓小偷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Parking tickets and purse snatchers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我以前的活比起来没什么挑战性  奎恩先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}aren't exactly a challenge after my old job, Mr. Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我阿伦佐就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Alonzo, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上次见面的时候  你说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The last time we met, you said
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀疑我教子的谋杀案有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}you had suspicions about my godson's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着跟进几条线索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I tried working a few leads,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  卡尔的部门档案被封了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but Cal's department file was sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种可能是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There is a chance here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟HR组织有关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that the organization HR could be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HR\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}HR?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为HR已经解体了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I thought HR was disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局只是抓了些小喽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The Feds just scattered the roaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难把他们一网打尽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's sometimes hard to get 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许可以让市长介入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Maybe I can get the mayor involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫警察厅总部配合下你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}open doors for you at 1 PP.
