Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古董商的生意怎么会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And what business does an antique dealer have
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟HR的洗钱扯上关系呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}laundering HR's money in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么现在要他死呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And why do they want him dead now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来瑞典人并没有找到真正的治疗师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Turns out the Swede wasn't going to a real therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他全透给了一个骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was spilling his guts to a con man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来一个买一送一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We'll do a two for one special
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把治疗师一起解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and take out the therapist also.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这晚餐是个大惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, that dinner was such a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I had a lovely time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是唯一的惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's not the only surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发吧  娜塔莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Let's do it, Nat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Let's take our trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去机场  选个目的地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just go to the airport and pick our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登  你是认真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hayd, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们的工作  生活怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What about our-- our jobs, our lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来之后  一切照样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They'll be here for us when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想冲动一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I wanna be impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和心爱的姑娘浪迹天涯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I wanna whisk away the girl I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  当然好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候动身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When do we leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是另一个惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's the other surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  不  明天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now. No, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有些事情要做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I need to do a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上去接你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Pick you up in the A.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会火速打包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll pack fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  那骗子马上要出国了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch, our con man's blowing the country fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Something's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Wait, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守夜人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The night watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who were these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察  真警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The cops-- the real cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正打算问你呢  海登\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We were gonna ask you the same thing, Hayden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚和卡特警探通了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I just spoke with Detective Carter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她认出你给我的警徽号码是HR的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She identified the badge numbers you gave me as HR.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She's positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What's the deal, con man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚有人把我的办公室搅了个天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Look. Someone just turned my office into Swiss cheese,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女朋友还在等我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and my girlfriend is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她去我家  或者我办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If she goes back to my place or to my office--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我半小时前和娜塔莉联系过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I just spoke to Natalie a half an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉她  我是你的新助手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I explained to her how I was your new assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安排她去旅馆藏起来  等你去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I needed to stash her in a motel until you'd visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Slight lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你的截然不同  海登\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But nothing on a par with you, Hayden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话出自你口真有意思  冉先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's funny coming from you, Mr. Wren.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道你一直在骗你的病人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We know you've been scamming your patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也知道你特别关注梵格先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and we know you've had your eye especially on a Mr. Vanger,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那名古董商\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}the antique dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他为HR洗钱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Did you know he was a money launderer for HR?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说过HR  但我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've heard of HR, but I swear,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是他们的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't know the money was theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你觉得你在骗谁的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who'd you think you were grifting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凡几个月前来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sven came into my office a couple of months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个烟鬼  账户里有几百万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was a chain smoker who had millions bouncing around in his accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本该很容易得手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It would have been an easy score.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果你瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Look what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没打算遇着真枪实弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't sign up for real bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干这单了  我要离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm done with this con and I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜塔莉在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where's Natalie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美  哪儿都别去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nice try. You're staying put.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了我不干这单了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What don't you get about "done"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想让我出城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Look. You want me out of town?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就出城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不会扔下她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I can't go without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我生命中  唯一的真诚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}See, she's the only honest thing left about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须紧紧抓住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I have to try and hold on to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警探  你发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Detective, have you found out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古董商和HR洗钱的联系了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}how the antique dealer is connected to HR's money laundering?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在找路子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm meeting my source now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一口酒都没尝  乔丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You haven't touched your wine, Joss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你下班了  -我从来不下班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- You're off duty. - I'm always on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到我说的了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Have you heard a word I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗钱这事儿你怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What do you think about the money being laundered?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听得清清楚楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I heard every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那笔钱是HR从俄罗斯人那里敲来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And the money's just HR's skim off the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一部分会给你那些制服朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A percentage kicked back to your friends in blue
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买他们对约格洛夫的生意睁只眼闭只眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}for turning a blind eye to the Yogorov business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请品尝一下蒙达奇诺布鲁尼洛干红\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Please, try the Brunello di Montalcino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,余味非常美妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The finish is quite exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HR从一个古董商手里能得到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}is what HR wants with an antique business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干净的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Clean money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  HR不想要俄罗斯人血淋淋的脏钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}See, HR doesn't want blood-soaked bills from the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要把到手的钱化整为零\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They want their cut in ones and zeroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转入他们的退休金账户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to transfer into their 401ks,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离岸账户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}offshore accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  古董商先把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, the antique dealer cycles
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯人的黑钱放入自己的账户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}the dirty Russian money into his own accounts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待指令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and waits for instructions.
