Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括卢・格里克和贝比・鲁斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}including Lou Gehrig and Babe Ruth.
