Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前边这位440万一次  两次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}4.4 in the front going once, twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成交  440万  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sold right here, $4.4 million. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞典人出价最高  这样所有的黑钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The Swede bids the highest, and all of that dirty money
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就都转到HR名下了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}is deposited into HR's coffers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干净利落地洗白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Squeaky clean and laundered,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以转账\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and ready for digital distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没有洗钱啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They haven't laundered the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只买了个超贵的棒球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They've just bought an overpriced baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有HR的拍品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All the items HR auctions off
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽拍价高达上百万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}may have been appraised for millions of dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实都是假货  赝品  不值钱的垃圾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but they're really just fugazis, fakes, worthless junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以HR就白拿了俄罗斯人的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So HR gets Russian money for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这系统天衣无缝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's a perfect system,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非外边有人窥破天机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}till someone on the outside knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那骗子以为自己能插手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So if your con man thinks he can just swoop in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分HR的一杯羹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and take a piece of HR's business,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就得小心点了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He better watch his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是过来见谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who do you always meet in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不关你事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.75,0:22:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特  我一直在想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Carter, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个古董商\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That antique dealer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能就这么杀人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can't just kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当初进HR时  我没想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When I got involved with HR, I didn't think--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想  你是没想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, you didn't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就睁只眼闭只眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You just looked the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再那样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can't do that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有你跟我同路了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And you're the only person I've got on my side right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不跟你同路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也不能眼睁睁看着命案发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I'm also not letting a homicide happen under my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天  你给我请病假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, tomorrow, you're calling in sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  给你个新任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah, see you just got a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天  给我跟踪西蒙斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tomorrow, you're Simmons's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去哪  你就去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Wherever he goes, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管见谁  你都要拍照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Whoever he meets with, you get pictures of.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚发现他们的储钱罐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}See, we just tapped into their piggy bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道谁在掌管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now I wanna know who's running the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.95,0:23:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  吓人的家伙是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What-- who is that creepy guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜塔莉  对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Natalie, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你办公室有人给我打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I get a call from someone at your office
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去什么酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}telling me to come to some hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本没露面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and then you don't even show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  深呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's okay. You need to take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:23:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着呼吸  慢慢平静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The more you breathe, the calmer you'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  不许催眠我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, no, no. Do not hypno-talk me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没催眠你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not hypno-talking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  平静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm saying, just be calm--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你的病人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not one of your patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know that, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You have to tell me--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  你觉不觉得我们的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch, you ever notice how much of our job
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像当保姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}is like babysitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可不止如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's more than that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:24:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登似乎没把骗局对我们和盘托出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't think Hayden's told us the whole story of his con.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在查看海登的硬盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm going over Hayden's hard drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.04,0:24:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在他销毁前下载的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}what I downloaded of it before he zapped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现了古董商斯凡・梵格的邮箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I'm finding emails addressed to Sven Vanger, the antique dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.18,0:24:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hayden may have elicited
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他催眠时套出了邮箱密码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}his email password while he was under hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.39,0:24:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来海登复制的这封邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It appears that Hayden duplicated an email
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.49,0:24:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凡虽收到了  却还没读\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that Sven had received, but not yet read.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.26,0:24:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他修改了内容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And he altered it in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.81,0:24:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮件什么内容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And what did the email say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.72,0:24:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮件来自匿名地址\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The email is from an anonymous address,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.00,0:24:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提起今天有一场拍卖会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}regarding an auction that took place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里边要求梵格去竞拍424号拍品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}In it, Vanger was instructed to bid on lot 424,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.91,0:24:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是海登修改了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But Hayden redrafted it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.50,0:24:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要他去拍426号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}instructing him to bid on lot 426.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.21,0:24:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许该去问问海登为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Perhaps you should ask Hayden why.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.58,0:25:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跳窗户出去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He went out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.65,0:25:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  海登利用他女朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch, Hayden used his girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.19,0:25:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷溜走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and gave us all the slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.89,0:25:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我要打烊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry. I'm about to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.60,0:25:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  斯凡  你已经打烊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, Sven, you're already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪边的  俄罗斯人的还是警察的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who are you with, the Russians or the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.97,0:25:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没东西给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I have nothing left for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.01,0:25:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两边都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not with either.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.64,0:25:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来是要个东西  答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I do need something-- answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.96,0:25:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会任人宰割\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not your doormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.60,0:25:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下枪别伤了自己吧  斯凡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Why don't you drop that before you hurt yourself, Sven?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.65,0:25:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.00,0:25:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么最近你一打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Why is it every time you call me these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.24,0:25:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道得带枪呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know to bring a firearm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.75,0:26:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个好治疗师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But he was such a good therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.73,0:26:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙纹男\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Dragon tattoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.22,0:26:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是个把你的钱全偷走的骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}he's also a con man who stole from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.02,0:26:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的钱  是他们的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not stealing from me, stealing from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.67,0:26:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真不该那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He should not be doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.79,0:26:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么搅进这趟浑水的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How'd you even get into this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.34,0:26:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七个月前  纽约海关要找我麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Seven months ago, I got in trouble with the customs here in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.26,0:26:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名叫西蒙斯的警察来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A cop named Simmons came
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.64,0:26:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他可以摆平那些指控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and said he could make the charges go away
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.57,0:26:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我帮他们的俄罗斯合伙人洗钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}if I helped them launder cash for a few Russian associates of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.14,0:26:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始  每月也就是几十万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}At first, it was just a few hundred thousand each month.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.37,0:26:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后数目越来越大  几百万了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then it became more and more-- millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.73,0:26:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天刚甩掉最后一笔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I got rid of the last cash today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.14,0:26:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,426号拍品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}On Lot 426?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.36,0:26:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How did you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.50,0:26:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登耍了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hayden played you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.90,0:26:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他篡改了你的电子邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He switched out your emails,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.97,0:26:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你今天拍错了东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and made you bid on the wrong item today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.92,0:26:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我买的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then what did I purchase?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.02,0:26:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A real ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.72,0:26:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,签有1927年洋基队真迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}signed by the real 1927 Yankees,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.15,0:26:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正价值440万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}really worth 4.4 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.71,0:26:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那年头儿是真牛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That was a hell of a season.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.20,0:26:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球在哪儿  斯凡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where's the ball, Sven?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.91,0:26:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.43,0:26:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卖掉了  就五美元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I sold it for $5.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.27,0:27:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会干掉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They're going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.95,0:27:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得赶快跑路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I gotta get out of this city immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.72,0:27:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太晚了  你已经被盯上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Too late. You're a marked man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.11,0:27:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把眼睛闭上  这玩意辣眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Close your eyes. This stuff burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.97,0:27:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在都开始伪造犯罪现场了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So we're faking crime scenes now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.00,0:27:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在第八分局时真有差距啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A long way from your days back at the Eighth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.12,0:27:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得往边上撒点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Might wanna spread it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.81,0:27:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动脉出血喷得比较分散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arterial spray is more erratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.62,0:27:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我干活儿成不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Will you let me work?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要伪装成一种独特的中弹效果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Going for a kind of a hollow-point special kind of motif.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.57,0:27:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了  -恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- There. - Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.62,0:27:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚死而复生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You've just died and been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.52,0:27:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  珍惜生命  滚出纽约\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now, take your new life, and get the hell out of New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.15,0:27:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}短信\N来自卡特\N告诉西蒙斯你搞定瑞典人了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.86,0:27:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HC2C2B4&\fs16\frz-25\pos(243.97,155.571)}来电\N{\b1}西蒙斯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.71,0:27:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.33,0:27:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Rookie,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.32,0:28:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先别干掉那古董商\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I need you to hold off on the antique dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.41,0:28:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍卖行那里出了点问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Something went wrong at the auction house.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.05,0:28:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没拿到钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We didn't get our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.98,0:28:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  有点小问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sir, there's a small problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.07,0:28:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在HR的线人刚传来消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just heard from my source in HR,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.12,0:28:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙斯知道他们上当了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Simmons knows they get ripped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.21,0:28:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说棒球的事儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All this baseball stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.17,0:28:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该早点来找我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}you should've called me in sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.67,0:28:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是大都会队的粉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm kind of a Mets fan, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.67,0:28:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}洋基队和大都会队两支同为纽约棒球队
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.17,0:28:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市的某个角落  某个小屁孩的兜里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Somewhere in the city, your soda kid's walking around
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.98,0:28:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正装着那颗价值连城的棒球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}with a zillion-dollar baseball in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.24,0:28:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HR正在找那个球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}With HR looking for the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.33,0:28:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小孩却对此一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And the young man has no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.37,0:28:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他别拿来练接球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Let's hope he don't play catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.99,0:28:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子  有我的东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Kiddo, you got something for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.93,0:29:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信海登会利用自己的女友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can't believe Hayden would use his own girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.02,0:29:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借机逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}as an excuse to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.59,0:29:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信  价值四百万的棒球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can. A baseball worth 4 million
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.50,0:29:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引力可不小\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}would be a motivational force.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.88,0:29:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不在乎自己逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He doesn't care who he steps on
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.33,0:29:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会连累多少人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to get away with it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.58,0:29:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是  他仍要逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Exactly. He still has to get away,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.19,0:29:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他不会扔下娜塔莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but he won't go without Natalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.78,0:29:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我都非常清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}As you and I well know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理性与感性常常相互冲突\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}sometimes necessity and desire can conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.36,0:29:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登还在城里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hayden's still in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.75,0:29:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会蠢到用自己的手机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He's too smart to use his own phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.64,0:29:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们怎么追踪他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So how do we track him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.32,0:29:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管他  我们追踪娜塔莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We don't. We track Natalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.17,0:29:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海登正在给她打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hayden's calling her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.33,0:29:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜  拜托  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nat, please, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.45,0:29:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实做过不应该的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've done things that I'm not proud of,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.09,0:29:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.38,0:29:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Can you trust me on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.55,0:29:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道现在到底是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I wanna know what's going on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.91,0:29:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况有点复杂  娜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's a little complicated, Nat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.44,0:29:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-等等  你在哪儿  -回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Wait. Where are you? - I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.90,0:29:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你跳窗户出去之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Did you think I was just gonna sit in that hotel room
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.30,0:29:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会待在那酒店房间里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}after you went out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  亲爱的  你不能回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, honey, you can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.80,0:29:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's not safe for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.63,0:29:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  我怎么会知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Really? How would I even know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.08,0:29:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  海登  我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Look, Hayden, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.02,0:30:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我得知道真相  否则算了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I deserve the truth, or else I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.48,0:30:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是罪犯  是贼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm a criminal and a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.06,0:30:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不再干了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I'm done with that life.
