Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.83,0:31:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许该让那个菜鸟来帮你善后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Maybe the rookie should be handling your end of things.
