Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.09,0:31:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出了骗子的小女朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}we found out about the con man's little girlfriend.
