Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.12,0:32:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所说  你是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Like you said, you're a crook.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.58,0:32:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是啥专家  不过看起来挺真\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't know about expert, but it looks pretty damn real.
