Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.96,0:32:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们至少容我打个电话给娜塔莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Will you at least let me call Natalie
