Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.85,0:32:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让你失望了  骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sorry to disappoint, con man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.06,0:32:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来纽约警局的电话追踪技术不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Seems the NYPD isn't bad at phone traces.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.02,0:32:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我20分钟内就找到你女友了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I found your girl in 20 minutes.
