Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.16,0:33:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过棒球我还是要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I'll take the ball, just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.05,0:33:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20分钟后在拍卖行门前见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You meet me in front of the auction house in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.25,0:33:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况多糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.96,0:33:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会杀死她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.69,0:33:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人  为了这么一大笔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}These people, for this much money?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.99,0:33:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你打算怎么阻止他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So what are you gonna do to stop them?
