Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.63,0:33:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可娜塔莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But Natalie--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的终极骗局  最后一笔是为了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My ultimate con, my final trick was gonna be
