Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.42,0:33:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都可以放弃  只要能救她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll give it all away to save her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.18,0:33:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会帮我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.25,0:33:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么安排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This is how it goes.
