Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.08,0:33:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这个小丑我不能再冒险了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not taking any more chances with this clown.
