Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.98,0:34:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女友呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.39,0:34:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和娜塔莉说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I wanna talk to Natalie.
