Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.68,0:34:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只相信  一日为贼  终身为贼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}One thing you can trust about a thief is he'll always be a thief.
