Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.26,0:34:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱和尸体搞定后给我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Call me when there's money and bodies.
