Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.73,0:41:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我紧紧跟着那家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I stuck to the guy like glue.
