Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.86,0:41:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了  孩子  你做得不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Thanks, kid, you did all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.19,0:41:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要知道  情况会越来越严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But you should know, it'll get harder out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.67,0:41:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过这几天的事儿  事态会升级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}After these last few days, things are gonna heat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.58,0:41:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So you need to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.61,0:41:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入HR时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When I got involved with HR,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.77,0:41:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自以为它代表忠诚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I thought it was about loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.79,0:41:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.53,0:41:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实它只有谋杀和贪婪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's about murder and greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.02,0:41:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勾结上了啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ain't that cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.69,0:41:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早该知道她会策反你  菜鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I should've known she'd turn you, rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.35,0:41:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见你  我就知道你软弱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The first time I saw you, I knew you were weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.17,0:41:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我告诉你个真实的世界吧  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So let me tell you how the world works now, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.82,0:42:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么我们杀了她  要么他们杀了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We kill her or they kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.17,0:42:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将是你的最后决定  铁尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That decision is gonna be your last, Terney.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.56,0:42:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.76,0:42:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Laskey?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.19,0:42:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流这么多血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That much blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.48,0:42:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能撑一分钟了  最多两分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and you'll be dead in a minute, maybe two.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.52,0:42:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死得有价值点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Make 'em count.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.96,0:42:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和西蒙斯向谁汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who do you and Simmons report to?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.20,0:42:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁发号施令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who calls the shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.71,0:42:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案在这些照片里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Is the answer in these pictures, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.27,0:42:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后机会了  铁尼  拿出警察样来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Last chance, Terney! Be a cop!

